verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Precious Lord, take my hand, lead me on,
Help me stand;
I am tired, I am weak, I am worn;
Thru the storm, thru the night,
Lead me on to the light,
Take my hand, precious Lord, lead me home.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}When my way grows drear, precious Lord,
Linger near;
When my life is almost gone,
Hear my cry, hear my call, hold my hand
Lest I fall;
Take my hand, precious Lord, lead me home.{/lang-eng}
